<TEXT>
Vera Weisfeld, retail entrepreneur.
I want to see the police taking the emphasis off the motorist and going after
the knife killers and the drugs dealers and all the other crime. I stand
outside my store and I see mothers with their shopping and their two children,
and their car has been taken away, and all they've done is park in the wrong
place. And, now the Bosnian situation is resolving itself, I would like this
year to be a year of peace. I would love to see the countries get together and
do something about peace.
</TEXT>
