iscount of up to 25%. These are flexible fares allowing bookings to be changed
and no Saturday night restrictions. This applies to Edinburgh/Glasgow services
to London, East Midland, Leeds and Copenhagen and Heathrow to Dublin and Prague
services. Call 03
45 554 554.
