before January 31 there's a cash-back deal. Other special offers include free
hotel nights. Sample pr
ices are LA, Australia and Hawaii for #1494 for 17 days, and New Zealand and a
cruise round the Bay of Islands, Rotorua, Queenstown and Christchurch for #2081
for 17 days and children go free (one child under 12 years for two adults).
Travel agents have b
rochures or call 0990 555757.
n SHEARINGS have introduced a coach tour to Ireland in the '96 brochure. Prices
